Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}是时候了 去召集军团吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Summon the legions. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们的敌人扬言要发起进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy vows to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你们当中有谁愿意奋起作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who among you will stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你们会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这一天我已经等待很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long have I awaited this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我向索隆宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pledge my loyalty to Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们的人已经走了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half of us just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但还有一半选择了留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But half stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}为什么没有选我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why wasn't I chosen for the expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我以为你要去西部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you were going west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我要先做点配得上努门诺尔人做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not till I've done something worthy of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我刚刚说服努门诺尔派出五艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have just convinced Númenor to send five ships
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}和五百人来帮助你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and 500 men to aid your people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}帮你加冕为王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and place a crown upon your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你是在要我去一个 我发誓永远不会回去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are asking me to go to the one place that I swore never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你为什么要一直战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}因为我停不下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I cannot stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}跟我一起去 一起拯救我们俩的种族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me, and together we will redeem both our bloodlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们朝东北方向行进 前往中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We head nor'-east. For Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这并不是剑 而是一种力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is no sword. It is a power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你听说过索隆吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我以前见过这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这是一把钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}敌方指挥官说过 要在这些土地上给奥克一个家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The enemy commander spoke of giving the Orcs a home in these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但不管他有什么阴谋 有一点是肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever his design, this much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}敌人知道你儿子 有他需要用来启动计划的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy knows your son has what he needs to enact it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}可能是几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}指环王：力量之戒\N第一季第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\fn微软雅黑\b1}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}新生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}蔑视死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In defiance of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们经受了艰辛无数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have endured much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们挣脱了枷锁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cast off our shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}越过高山和原野\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crossed mountain, field,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}穿过严寒和荒地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}frost, and fallow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}直到我们脚上的血染湿了地上的泥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}till our feet bloodied the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}从灰色山脉到埃斐尔阿尔能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Ered Mithrin to the Ephel Arnen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们都坚持下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但今晚 还有一场考验在等着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet tonight, one more trial awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}或许敌人实力很弱 而且为数不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy may be weak, their numbers meager...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但明天黎明之前 我们当中会有一部分奥克倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...yet before this night is through, some of us will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但如果你们这次倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}将不再是远方大地上籍籍无名的奴隶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you do so not as unnamed slaves in far-away lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}而是首次以兄弟的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but as brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}以兄弟姐妹的身份 在属于我们自己的土地上倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As brothers and sisters in our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat! Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}因为就在今夜 我们将伸出乌鲁克族的铁拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the night we reach out the iron hand of the Uruk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}握紧双拳夺回这片土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and close our fist around these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}给我搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Search it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}全体注意 散开 把他们找出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you! Fan out! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}父亲大人 我无意冒犯 但敢问索隆在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning no offense, Lord-father, but where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}找不到他的丝毫踪迹 他肯定是学聪明逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't find tooth nor tail of him. Must've got smart and scarpered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}不会的 那个精灵就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The Elf's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我闻到他的气味了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I smell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}遵命 父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}在这上边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}把他拿下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}马上撤出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}把那扇门打开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}快出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}父亲大人 您得立刻离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord-father! You must move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}您得离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这么大的火 能侥幸活下来的奥克能有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many of 'em could have survived that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们有多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}并没有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}来吧 我们得把村子武装起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, we have to make ready the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}慢点 贝雷克 别激动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, Berek. Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}把它吊起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hoist it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我以为所有士兵都上床睡觉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought all soldiers were to be abed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}请原谅我 指挥官 我只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pardon me, Commander. I... I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}想第一个看到大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hoping to get the first sight of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}稍息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}过一会儿你就能看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be visible to your eyes in a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}难道说你已经看到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it visible to yours already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}大约一个小时前我就看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has been for nearly an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}精灵的眼神真是犀利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keen are the eyes of the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}可是我却从没见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet, mine have not before seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}没见过你舞剑也没见过你扬帆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swinging steel nor flying sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你是什么军衔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is your rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我负责清扫马厩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}不要瞧不起这种 能让人学会谦逊的劳苦工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despise not the labor which humbles the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}对于整个王国来说 满招损谦受益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humility has saved entire kingdoms the proud have all but led to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我加入远征军 可不是为了来学习谦逊的 指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not join this expedition to be humbled, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那你加入的目的是什么 士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then for what did you join, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我只是想离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just trying to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}尽可能远离那个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As far as I could from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}努门诺尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Númenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}不是努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}反正不是真正的努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the real Númenor, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}真正的努门诺尔根本没存在过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}它存在过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}而且仍然存在…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It exists still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}哪怕只存在于最下层的 马厩清洁工心里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only in the heart of the lowliest stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我叫伊熙尔杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我早该看出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你长得像你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have the look of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}人们总说我长得更像我母亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was always told I look more like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}船长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他母亲…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}她出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我大半辈子 望向东方都是见旭日从海面上升起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of my life, I've looked east to see the Sun rise over the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}望向西方见夕阳落到地平线下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And west to see it set over the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}虽然我们正驶向黎明 但对我而言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're sailing into the dawn, and yet, to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}感觉却像夜幕即将降临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it feels like the coming of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}她是淹死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}已经看到陆地了 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Land has been sighted, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们多久才能抛锚停泊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long before we make anchor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}要航行一整天才能进入山区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a full day's sail into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}从那里出发 要向东再骑一天才能进入山谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And from there, another day's ride east into the vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}给其他船发信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Signal the other ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}告诉他们尽可能加快速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them to make all possible haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}以我们的能力无法毁掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is beyond our skill to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你要把它藏在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where will you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}不能让任何人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}就连你也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们已经发现了敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy has been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}上一次我们活了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We survived them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这次我们也必将战胜敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we must do so again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们的位置很有利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our position gives us an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但要想利用这个优势 必须把敌人引到近处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to use it, we must draw the enemy in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们必须等到所有奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must wait until every last Orc
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}跨过那座桥之后 再发起进攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has crossed that bridge to spring our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这将会考验你们的勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will test your nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}放马过来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}所有无法战斗的人员将在里边驻守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All who cannot fight will be barricaded inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这里将是我们的要塞和撤退据点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is to be our keep. Our fallback point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}大家都要鼓起勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Take heart. All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我见过许多军队以少胜多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have seen smaller armies defeat greater foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}太阳很快就要落山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, the sun will set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我向你们保证 只要守好自己的岗位 就能见到明天的日出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do your part, and I swear to you, you shall see it rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-你们相信吗  -相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you believe it? -Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-你们相信吗  -相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you believe it? -Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}各就各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你去小酒馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}伤员和儿童才去小酒馆 我可以战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern's for wounded and children. I can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我知道你可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}所以我才要你去那里 保护无法战斗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I need you in there, protecting those who cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我小时候经常会做各种噩梦 你记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember when I was little... When I used to have bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}还记得你是怎么安慰我的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember what you used to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}就是你在黑暗中抱着我说的那番话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you would hold me in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}现在能再说给我听吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you say it to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}“魔影终究只是渺小之物 且会逝去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"In the end, this shadow is but a small and passing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}“而在魔影无法触及之处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There is light and high beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}“光明与崇高之美永存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"forever beyond its reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}“去寻找光明吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Find the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}“如此魔影便永远不得临身”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And the shadow will not find you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}再见 妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farewell, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}没有 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}阿尔费林种子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The alfirin seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这是精灵的一项传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a tradition among Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}每逢战争开始之前 种下一颗阿尔费林种子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before the battle begins, plant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}新生命 蔑视死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New life, in defiance of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}精灵族相信 有一位维拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is believed that one of the Valar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}会照看生长的植物…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watches over growing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}以及植物的播种者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And those who tend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}其余的种子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们等战争结束后再来种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we shall plant after the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}种在一个新花园里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a new garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}还有希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们一起种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}一言为定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我的天…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那群蠢货没打中我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bleeding fools missed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他们正朝小酒馆走去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're headed for the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-为南方大地而战  -为南方大地而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fight for the Southlands! -Fight for the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这片土地是我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The land is ours!
