Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.75,0:45:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那安塔摩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Ontamo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我想我可能会 在这里待一阵子 帮帮这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I might stay here for a while. Lend these folk a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-这周的战争看够了  -恐怕是一辈子的战争都看够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Seen enough battle for a week? -More like a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.25,0:46:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这支军队什么时候出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This company, when's it set out?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.70,0:46:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}还不确定 要等加拉德瑞尔先处理完阿达尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know for certain. Not till she's done with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.54,0:46:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我小的时候 听过很多精灵被魔苟斯带走的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was a child, I heard stories of Elves taken by Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那些精灵被折磨 被扭曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tortured. Twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他们被改造为 一种新的 被摧残的生命形式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made into a new and ruined form of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.58,0:46:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你就是其中一员吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are one of them, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.75,0:46:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}魔里昂多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Moriondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.00,0:46:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}黑暗之子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Sons of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.83,0:46:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}第一批奥克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.50,0:46:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}乌鲁克族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.04,0:46:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我们更喜欢自称“乌鲁克族”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We prefer "Uruk."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.54,0:46:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}就连魔里昂多也是听令于主人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even Moriondor take orders from a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.08,0:46:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我要找你的主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I seek yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.62,0:46:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.91,0:46:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}索隆在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.08,0:47:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}或许我们应该让囚犯们晒晒太阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we should bring our prisoners into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.54,0:47:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}魔苟斯战败后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After Morgoth's defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你们称之为索隆的那一位…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the one you call Sauron...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.79,0:47:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}致力于“治愈”中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Devoted himself to healing Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.75,0:47:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}将被毁坏的土地 以完美的秩序重新聚拢在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bringing its ruined lands together in perfect order.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.83,0:47:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他试图打造一种力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He sought to craft a power
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.70,0:47:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}并非来源于肉体…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not of the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.83,0:47:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}而是让肉体受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.70,0:47:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}一种不可见世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A power of the Unseen World.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他说服尽可能多的人随他向北行进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He bid as many as he could to follow him far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.91,0:48:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但虽然他竭尽所能…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But try as he might...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他还是缺少一样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.54,0:48:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那就是黑暗知识的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A shadow of dark knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.12,0:48:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}一直隐藏着 就是不让他找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that kept itself hidden, even from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.37,0:48:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}哪怕他在求索的过程中 手上已经沾满无数鲜血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how much blood he spilt in its pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}对我来说…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mmm. For my part...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.58,0:48:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}为了帮助他实现愿望 我已经牺牲了足够多的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sacrificed enough of my children for his aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.50,0:48:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我把索隆撕碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I split him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.04,0:49:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I killed Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.79,0:49:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我不信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.08,0:49:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你的整支军队都杀不掉索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot believe an Uruk could do that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.29,0:49:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你当然不信一个乌鲁克就能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which your entire army could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.87,0:49:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我不相信你是这支军队唯一的主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot believe that you are this army's only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.95,0:49:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我的孩子们没有主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children have no master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他们不是孩子 是奴隶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are not children, they are slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但他们每一个都有姓名 有内心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But each one has a name. A heart. A heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.37,0:49:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-由魔苟斯创造的内心 -我们都出自独一之神的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A heart created by Morgoth. -We are creations of The One,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.87,0:49:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}出自秘火的主宰 跟你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Master of the Secret Fire, the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}他们也值得拥有生命之息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As worthy of the breath of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.33,0:49:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}也同样值得拥有家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and just as worthy of a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.16,0:49:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}很快…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.70,0:49:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这片土地将会是我们的 到时候你就会明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This land will be ours. Then, you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.87,0:49:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你族群的存在就是个错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your kind was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}一群拙劣的仿制品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made in mockery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.29,0:50:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}哪怕要花上一整个纪元 我也会发誓要将你们斩草除根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even if it takes me all of this Age, I vow to eradicate every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.45,0:50:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但我会让你活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you shall be kept alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.25,0:50:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}好让你见证那一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.95,0:50:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}到时候我会用匕首刺入你中毒的心脏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before I drive my dagger into your poisoned heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.16,0:50:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我会在你尖尖的耳朵旁低语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will whisper in your piked ear
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.25,0:50:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你的后代已经死绝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that all your offspring are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你种族的祸根将以你为终结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the scourge of your kind ends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}看来我不是唯一一个还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would seem I'm not the only Elf alive
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.70,0:50:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但已经被黑暗所改变的精灵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who has been transformed by darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.79,0:50:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}也许你苦苦寻找的魔苟斯继任者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps your search for Morgoth's successor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.37,0:50:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}会在你的镜子里寻见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should have ended in your own mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.70,0:51:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}也许我应该先杀了你 你这个奥克的奴隶贩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps I shall begin by killing you, you slavering Orc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.50,0:51:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}加拉德瑞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.58,0:51:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}乌鲁克…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.37,0:51:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.12,0:52:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}谢谢你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.16,0:52:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}把我拉了回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For pulling me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.79,0:52:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}早前是你先把我拉了回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was you, pulled me back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.50,0:52:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}不管他对你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever it was he did to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.87,0:52:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}也不管你做了什么…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and whatever it was you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.58,0:52:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}都要放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be free of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.66,0:52:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我从不相信我能放下…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never believed I could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.08,0:52:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}直到今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.95,0:53:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}与你并肩作战 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fighting at your side, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.29,0:53:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我感觉…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.25,0:53:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}如果我能抓住这种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I could just hold on to that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.12,0:53:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}时刻保留在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}keep it with me always,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.04,0:53:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}并将它深深刻入我的灵魂 那么我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bind it to my very being, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.54,0:53:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我也感觉到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.66,0:53:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}哈尔布兰德大人 摄政女王想见您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lord Halbrand. The Queen Regent wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.91,0:54:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}摄政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.41,0:54:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我欠你的…你让我的人民得以幸存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I owe you... My people are alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.00,0:54:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}按照我的理解 他们之所以能活着是因为你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I understand it, they're alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我可没想过要扛起这份重担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A burden I never sought to take up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}只有极少数最优秀的领袖 才能扛此重任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few of the finest leaders do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.04,0:55:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但如果你想减轻这份负担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you would like some relief in carrying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.70,0:55:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我也许能帮上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.66,0:55:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}陛下 您找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You called for me, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.91,0:55:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}布隆温…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.58,0:55:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这位是哈尔布兰德大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Lord Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}布隆温\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.25,0:55:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}是真的吗  你就是他们承诺给我们的那位国王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true? Are you the king we were promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.66,0:55:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.20,0:56:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}所有人致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.37,0:56:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}向南方大地真正的国王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.33,0:56:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}向南方大地真正的国王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}向南方大地真正的国王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.91,0:56:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}这片土地上的人们 已经等待这一刻很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The men of these lands have awaited this moment a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.87,0:56:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}肯定没有精灵等得久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not nearly so long as the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.83,0:57:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}别折磨自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not torment yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.29,0:57:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}换做别人 很多人也会做同样的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many might have done the same in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.70,0:57:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.95,0:57:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我感到的不仅仅是内疚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just guilt I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.83,0:57:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}还有一种失去感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.91,0:57:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}失去感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}当它在我手中时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it was in my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.37,0:57:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我感觉…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.70,0:57:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}非常强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.08,0:57:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}那就摆脱掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then rid yourself of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.08,0:58:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}一劳永逸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.20,0:58:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}怎么摆脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.33,0:58:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}交给努门诺尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it to Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.70,0:58:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}让他们在返航回家的途中扔进海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To toss into the sea on their voyage home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.20,0:59:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}放轻松 贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Easy. Berek, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}划伤了一点而已 你没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a scratch. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.91,0:59:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}嘿…贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey. Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.54,0:59:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.20,0:59:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}帮帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Athae...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.20,1:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}冷静下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no ídhui hí.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.25,1:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你是怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.87,1:00:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}困扰它的并不是它身上的疼痛…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not his pain that's bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.50,1:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}而是骑手的疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that of his rider.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.91,1:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}我不觉得痛啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm not in pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.00,1:00:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}当西方之地努门诺尔的马匹 进入战场时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a horse of Westernesse rides into battle,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.79,1:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}它会与骑乘的战士 形成一种牢不可破的纽带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he forms an unbreakable bond with the soldier he bears.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.12,1:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}随着时间的推移 人马合一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In time, they become as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.33,1:00:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}甚至能够了解彼此的内心深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even knowing the innermost feelings of each other's heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.04,1:00:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-你了解它的感受  -不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know his feelings? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.62,1:00:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}但它了解你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.29,1:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你是从哪里学到这些的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you learn all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.58,1:00:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}从你妈妈那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.58,1:00:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}你能教我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think you could teach me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.33,1:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}乌顿…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ud?n... Ud?n. Ud?n.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.12,1:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}快找掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.87,1:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.87,1:03:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}贝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.75,1:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}维蓝迪尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.70,1:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}翻过墙去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the wall!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.00,1:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b1\fs18}-希奥  -希奥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! -Theo!
